name: Slide Puzzle
tagline: Website for Slidepuzzle windows app using javascript based library
body:
*** This is a website created using impress.js JavaScript library. This web page is used for advertising "Slide Puzzle" windows phone application. The Slide Puzzle is a creative effort of a team from Aalto and it can be found in the [Slide Puzzle](https://github.com/BuildIt2013/videopuzzle). For more information contact @sidtechnical Regards,
Sid
